name: Mandala 0.4.2 - 17 Vertices
description: A physics system, initiated with 17 vertices, created this image through the accumulation of the system's moment to moment state over time. This is a hi-res, printable image (31 × 22in). The generative visual system was developed as part of the performance piece MICHI: https://aaron-sherwood.com/works/michi/ Animation of how this image was generated available here: https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/86269
